PrecisAmendments to the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES which revise Article 207.02 (Compulsory Payments - General Provisions) so that members of all classes of the Reserve Force will be subject to the provisions concerning the garnishment of wages.

precis:
Amendments to the QUEEN'S REGULATIONS AND ORDERS FOR THE CANADIAN FORCES
which revise Article 207.02 (Compulsory Payments - General Provisions) so
that members of all classes of the Reserve Force will be subject to the
provisions concerning the garnishment of wages.
